## 🎯 Quick Navigation

### For New Contributors
1. Start with [ARCHITECTURE/](ARCHITECTURE/ARCHITECTURE.md)
2. Review [IMPLEMENTATION/IMPLEMENTATION_SUMMARY.md](IMPLEMENTATION/IMPLEMENTATION_SUMMARY.md)
3. Check [TESTING/COMPREHENSIVE_TESTING_GUIDE.md](TESTING/COMPREHENSIVE_TESTING_GUIDE.md)

### For Deployment
1. Read [DEPLOYMENT/DEPLOYMENT_CHECKLIST.md](DEPLOYMENT/DEPLOYMENT_CHECKLIST.md)
2. Follow [DEPLOYMENT/PRODUCTION_DEPLOYMENT.md](DEPLOYMENT/PRODUCTION_DEPLOYMENT.md)
3. Review [TESTING/QA_PRODUCTION_AUDIT.md](TESTING/QA_PRODUCTION_AUDIT.md)

### For Feature Development
1. Check relevant folder (e.g., [FEATURES/](FEATURES/) for colors, [LOGIN/](LOGIN/) for auth)
2. Review implementation docs
3. Follow testing guidelines

### For Integration Setup
1. Navigate to [INTEGRATIONS/](INTEGRATIONS/)
2. Select relevant integration (Email, HubSpot, etc.)
3. Follow setup steps

